tip.text: We prefer PSBC double IPA, passion fruit wheat ale (sour!),  and mulberry belgian wheat ale. Toasted coconut porter is weird.
Nashville hot chicken is really good! Beware tho, it's spicy.
Must try : jyo karubi (shio) and buta karubi (tare). Really good!!
Try the tsukemen! Dip ramen style. The soup is delicious. The noodle is different than their normal ramen. Gyoza also not bad.
First time eating here. It was pass 1 pm so only 2 people was eating there. The place is small. Only has around 8 seats. I ordered daichan ramen. The soup was thick and too salty! Price : 80k vnd.

venue.name: Dai Chan Japanese Noodle Shop 麺処 大ちゃん

tip.text: Try their fresh orange juice + ice cream! It's refreshing. Good to eat it on hot weather.
Try their dirty duck menu. Or if u cant eat duck, their fried chicken also good! It comes with saffron rice (nasi kuning) which tastes sooo good. I love the rice.

formattedAddress: Kawasan Pariwisata Nusa Dua BTDC Area lot C-0
location.address: Kawasan Pariwisata Nusa Dua BTDC Area lot C-0

tip.text: Try their award-winning maki roll. Their shrimp tempura was so-so. Salmon sashimi is great! Fresh. Salmon belly sashimi is the best! Maguro sashimi (tuna) also good! Salmon skin maki also great!
Their Crispy Garlic Calamary is a MUST! I always order it each time and never fail me.
Tried their kouign amann and latte and it was sooo good! Definitely come back again and try other thing!

formattedAddress: #B1-11/12 Raffles City Shopping Centre (252 North Bridge Rd.)

tip.text: Their crispy pork belly is good! The skin is soo crispy and the meat is tender. Eat it while still warm, it will melt in your mouth!
I like their new escargot recipe! Escargot with butter, garlic, tomato and cheese. They put the meat without shell now, and 1 portion is only 12 pcs. Before was 24 pcs xD But still worth it!
The place is okay for hangout. But i dont like the food here. Escargot tasted aweful, the worst escargot ever! Their pancake is ok, but the fruit was too sour. I prefer Koi Kemang than this place.

tip.text: Arrive early (before 8pm) to avoid waiting. Try sangria 500 ml for drink (can share). For food : mini hot dog, "jabugo" cured ham, baby squid "andaluza", cabreaos egg style.
